  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0da7 \u0d91\u0dad\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc1\u0dd4\u0db7\u0dcf\u0dc1\u0dd2\u0d82\u0dc3\u0db1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Congratulations to the new president",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The international community congratulated Mr. Ranil Wickramasinghe on his swearing in as the new president.",
        "The United States of America, Britain, New Zealand, Australia and the United Nations have congratulated President Ranil Wickremesinghe.",
        "The greetings generally included the hope that the government led by President Ranil Wickremesinghe will work to find solutions to the current economic and political crises while protecting democracy.",
        "It was also noted in those greetings that Sri Lanka needs economic reforms.",
        "The announcement issued by the United Nations states that it is essential for the new government and all parties to respect democracy, the rule of law, human rights, the right to peaceful assembly and the right to express opinions for a peaceful and stable Sri Lanka.",
        "It is also stated in the announcement that it is ready to work with the new president who was constitutionally appointed."
      ],
